I'm feeling quite humbled and overwhelmed, but thank you so much!

319
00:32:56,048 --> 00:32:58,248
ありがとうございます！
Thank you very much!

320
00:32:58,248 --> 00:33:03,448
Suaraさんには実は、4周年の時に逆凸でメッセージも頂戴しておりまして、
I actually received a message from Suara-san during my 4th anniversary call-in segment,

