Yes. Um, well, even from the staff at Aquaplus,

331
00:33:50,048 --> 00:33:53,648
「こよりさんっていう『うたわれ』配信してるよ」って言って、
they told me, "There's someone named Koyori-san streaming 'Utaware',"

332
00:33:53,648 --> 00:33:56,848
