555
00:45:22,072 --> 00:45:25,072
もういらない 嘘にただもがくなんて
I don't need it anymore, just struggling in lies...

556
00:45:25,072 --> 00:45:27,572
もったいないでしょ
it's such a waste, right?

557
00:45:27,572 --> 00:45:29,572
それぞれの物語
As our respective stories

558
00:45:29,572 --> 00:45:32,072
交差する瞬間を
intersect for a moment,

559
00:45:32,072 --> 00:45:37,572
見つめる秘密は...
the secret we gaze upon is...

560
00:45:44,272 --> 00:45:46,372
放て夢だけ
Release only your dreams,

561
00:45:46,372 --> 00:45:49,072
大きな声抱いて
holding a loud voice,

562
00:45:49,072 --> 00:45:53,072
弾けそうな煌めきも 消えることなく
the sparkle about to burst will never fade.

563
00:45:53,072 --> 00:45:56,072
どこまででも
To wherever it may be,

564
00:45:56,072 --> 00:45:58,572
世界の向こうに
to the other side of the world,

565
00:45:58,572 --> 00:46:00,872
届けてよ
deliver it!

566
00:46:00,872 --> 00:46:03,572
終わることのない
This heartbeat in my chest

567
00:46:03,572 --> 00:46:06,072
この胸の鼓動は
that will never end,

568
00:46:06,072 --> 00:46:08,572
どうしても どうしても
no matter what, no matter what,

569
00:46:08,572 --> 00:46:11,572
僕を呼んでいたから
because it was calling out to me.

570
00:46:11,572 --> 00:46:13,872
その先へと 走り続ける
Beyond that, I'll keep on running,

571
00:46:13,872 --> 00:46:17,072
次へ 次へと
to the next, and the next!

572
00:46:59,072 --> 00:47:01,072
全国制覇おめでとう！
[On-screen: Congratulations on winning the nationals!]

573
00:47:01,372 --> 00:47:03,072
妄想だっちゅうの
I say it's a delusion,

574
00:47:03,072 --> 00:47:04,572
中途半端な
going down a halfway

575
00:47:04,572 --> 00:47:07,072
深い坂下って
steep slope.

576
00:47:07,072 --> 00:47:10,072
脱ぎ尽くしていたと
The realistic eyes that had cast

577
00:47:10,072 --> 00:47:11,872
リアルな目はプレリュード
everything off are a prelude.

578
00:47:11,872 --> 00:47:13,172
何千回も
Thousands of times,

579
00:47:13,172 --> 00:47:14,372
何万回も
tens of thousands of times,

580
00:47:14,372 --> 00:47:17,372
いいように続けて君へ
to you who kept going in a good way,

581
00:47:17,372 --> 00:47:20,072
ねえ 聞かせてよ 夢はどんな音だって
hey, let me hear what sound your dream makes.

582
00:47:20,072 --> 00:47:22,072
諦めが完敗ならば
If giving up is a total defeat,

583
00:47:22,072 --> 00:47:25,072
絶対にないよ
it's definitely not happening.

584
00:47:25,072 --> 00:47:27,572
誰に邪魔させようと
No matter who tries to interfere,

585
00:47:27,572 --> 00:47:29,572
躊躇わないで
don't hesitate.

586
00:47:29,572 --> 00:47:32,072
たくさんの情熱を
Connect many passions

587
00:47:32,072 --> 00:47:34,572
落とさずに繋いでゆく
without ever dropping them,

588
00:47:34,572 --> 00:47:37,572
そう 最後まで
yes, until the very end.

589
00:47:44,272 --> 00:47:46,372
フラグに誓い
Swearing on the flag,

590
00:47:46,372 --> 00:47:49,072
惜しく弾けて
bursting regretfully,

591
00:47:49,072 --> 00:47:53,072
鳴り止まないファンファーレ
the fanfare that won't stop ringing,

592
00:47:53,072 --> 00:47:56,072
いつの心に
into the distant future

593
00:47:56,072 --> 00:47:58,572
流れていた
that was flowing

594
00:47:58,572 --> 00:48:00,872
遠い未来へ
in my heart at some point,

595
00:48:00,872 --> 00:48:02,572
祈るよ
I pray.

596
00:48:02,572 --> 00:48:05,072
忘れられない
Following and following

597
00:48:05,072 --> 00:48:07,572
あの日々の後悔を
the regrets of those days I can't forget,

598
00:48:07,572 --> 00:48:10,572
追いかけて 追いかけて
this feeling that slid in

599
00:48:10,572 --> 00:48:13,572
滑り込んだ この想い
overflowed into the blue sky,

600
00:48:13,572 --> 00:48:18,572
青い空に ふと溢れてた
suddenly and far away,

601
00:48:18,572 --> 00:48:21,072
遠く遠く
far, far away.

602
00:48:59,072 --> 00:49:02,572
目覚めては繰り返す
Waking up and repeating the cycle,

603
00:49:02,572 --> 00:49:05,072
眠い朝は
on sleepy mornings,

604
00:49:05,072 --> 00:49:08,572
襟のタイを
tightening the tie

605
00:49:08,572 --> 00:49:12,072
きつく締め
of my collar,

606
00:49:12,072 --> 00:49:15,572
教室のドア
passing through

607
00:49:15,572 --> 00:49:18,072
くぐると
the classroom door,

608
00:49:18,072 --> 00:49:21,572
ほんの少し
I can walk

609
00:49:21,572 --> 00:49:23,572
胸を張って
with a little

610
00:49:23,572 --> 00:49:25,572
歩き出せる
bit of pride.

611
00:49:25,572 --> 00:49:32,072
そんな日常に吹き抜ける風
In such an everyday life, a breeze blows through.

612
00:49:32,072 --> 00:49:35,072
聞こえた気がした
I felt like I heard it,

613
00:49:35,072 --> 00:49:38,072
感じた気がしたんだ
I felt like I sensed it.

614
00:49:38,072 --> 00:49:42,572
震え出す 今この胸で
Right now, in this trembling chest,

615
00:49:42,572 --> 00:49:46,072
もう来る気がした
I felt like it was already coming.

616
00:49:46,072 --> 00:49:50,072
幾億の星が消え去ってくのを
As billions of stars fade away,

617
00:49:50,072 --> 00:49:53,072
見送った
I saw them off,

618
00:49:53,072 --> 00:49:55,072
手を振った
waved goodbye,

619
00:49:55,072 --> 00:49:59,072
よかったねと
and said 'I'm glad for you'.

620
00:50:00,180 --> 00:50:02,180
手を振った
I waved my hand

621
00:50:02,180 --> 00:50:05,180
よかったねと
Saying, "Good for you"

622
00:50:07,880 --> 00:50:13,280
廊下の隅見下ろす 掃除の途中
I look down at the corner of the hallway in the middle of cleaning

623
00:50:14,380 --> 00:50:19,880
おかしなものだと思う
I think it's a strange thing

624
00:50:21,880 --> 00:50:27,280
あたしの中の時は止まってるのに
Even though the time inside of me has stopped

625
00:50:28,280 --> 00:50:33,780
違う日々を生きてるように
It feels like I'm living through different days

626
00:50:34,780 --> 00:50:40,280
誇りは雪のように降り積む
Dust falls and accumulates like snow

627
00:50:41,280 --> 00:50:44,280
待ってる気がした
I realized you're waiting

628
00:50:44,280 --> 00:50:47,780
呼んでる気がしたんだ
I realized you're calling

629
00:50:47,780 --> 00:50:54,080
震え出す今この時が
Now in this time that started to tremble

630
00:50:54,880 --> 00:50:57,880
見つけた気がした
I realized I found it

631
00:50:57,880 --> 00:51:03,080
失われた記憶が呼び覚ました
My lost memories recalled

632
00:51:03,080 --> 00:51:06,080
物語
My story

633
00:51:06,580 --> 00:51:09,580
永遠のその終わり
Of eternity, its ending

634
00:51:18,080 --> 00:51:21,080
昨日は遠く明日はすぐ
Yesterday was far away, tomorrow was right ahead

635
00:51:21,080 --> 00:51:26,580
そんな当たり前に心が踊った
That natural fact made my heart dance

636
00:51:28,580 --> 00:51:31,580
聞こえた気がした
I realized I heard it

637
00:51:31,580 --> 00:51:35,080
感じた気がしたんだ
I realized I felt it

638
00:51:35,080 --> 00:51:40,580
震え出す今この胸で
Now in my chest that started to tremble

639
00:51:40,580 --> 00:51:44,080
もう来る気がした
I realized it was coming already

640
00:51:44,580 --> 00:51:47,580
幾千の朝を越え
A new sun overcame thousands of mornings

641
00:51:47,580 --> 00:51:51,580
新しい日が
A new sun...

642
00:51:52,080 --> 00:51:55,080
待ってる気がした
I realized you're waiting

643
00:51:55,080 --> 00:51:58,580
呼んでる気がしたんだ
I realized you're calling

644
00:51:58,580 --> 00:52:04,080
震えてるこの魂が
My soul is trembling

645
00:52:04,080 --> 00:52:08,080
見つけた気がした
I realized I found it

646
00:52:08,080 --> 00:52:15,080
幾億の夢のように消え去れる日を
The day that's able to disappear like millions of dreams

647
00:52:15,380 --> 00:52:18,380
見送った
I saw off

648
00:52:18,380 --> 00:52:22,380
手を振った
I waved my hand

649
00:52:22,380 --> 00:52:28,080
ありがとうと
Saying, "Thank you"

650
00:53:44,080 --> 00:53:47,080
ぽつり灯り 管制塔
A faintly lit control tower

651
00:53:47,080 --> 00:53:50,080
砂嵐の向こうへ
Toward the other side of the sandstorm

652
00:53:50,080 --> 00:53:53,080
祈るように綴った
Written down like a prayer

653
00:53:53,080 --> 00:53:56,580
これからのこと
Things to come

