682
00:55:52,588 --> 00:55:55,388
「別に待ってないよ」
"I wasn't waiting at all"

683
00:55:56,288 --> 00:56:00,088
夢と呼んだそれもぼくだっただけ
It was just me who called it a dream

684
00:56:00,688 --> 00:56:04,288
もういいかい
Is it okay now?

685
00:56:05,188 --> 00:56:06,488
応えてよ、
Answer me,

686
00:56:06,488 --> 00:56:07,588
笑ってよ、
laugh for me,

687
00:56:07,588 --> 00:56:09,088
気付いてよ
notice me

688
00:56:09,388 --> 00:56:11,988
此処に居るのにな、
Even though I'm right here,

689
00:56:11,988 --> 00:56:15,088
意地悪だな
you're so mean

690
00:56:15,188 --> 00:56:17,588
誰にも届かない
Towards the light

691
00:56:17,588 --> 00:56:20,188
光を
that reaches no one

692
00:56:20,188 --> 00:56:22,588
ぼくだけは
I alone

693
00:56:22,588 --> 00:56:25,588
光と呼び続ける
will continue to call it light

694
00:56:26,588 --> 00:56:28,988
真夜中
In the middle of the night

695
00:56:28,988 --> 00:56:31,588
管制塔から
from the control tower

696
00:56:31,888 --> 00:56:35,088
あなたを明かしてやる
I will illuminate you

